#. TRANSLATORS: this is the first section of the description.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:103
msgid ""
"Secure boot prevents malicious software from being loaded when the device "
"starts. It is currently turned off."
msgstr ""
"セキュアブートはデバイスの起動時に悪意のあるソフトウェアが読み込まれることを"
"防ぎます。この機能は現在オフです。"

#. TRANSLATORS: this is the second section of the description.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-boot-dialog.c:106
msgid ""
"Secure boot can often be turned on from your device's UEFI firmware settings "
"(BIOS). For help, contact your hardware manufacturer or IT support provider."
msgstr ""
"セキュアブートは、多くの場合、UEFI ファームウェアの設定 (BIOS) から有効化でき"
"ます。サポートが必要な場合は、ハードウェアの製造元または IT サポート担当者に"
"お問い合わせください。"

#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.blp:54
msgid "_Copy Technical Report"
msgstr "技術的なレポートをコピーする(_C)"

#. TRANSLATORS: in reference to firmware protection: 0/4 stars
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:99
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.c:453
msgid "Security Checks Failed"
msgstr "セキュリティチェックに失敗"

#. TRANSLATORS: This is the description to describe the failure on
#. checking the security items.
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:102
msgid ""
"Hardware does not pass checks. This means that you are not protected against "
"common hardware security issues.\n"
"\n"
"It may be possible to resolve hardware security issues by updating your "
"firmware or changing device configuration options. However, failures can "
"stem from the physical hardware itself and may not be fixable."
msgstr ""
"ハードウェアはチェックに合格しませんでした。これは、一般的なハードウェアセ"
"キュリティの問題から保護されていないことを意味します。\n"
"\n"
"ファームウェアの更新やデバイスの設定オプションの変更により、ハードウェアセ"
"キュリティの問題を解決できる場合があります。ただし、物理的なハードウェア自体"
"に起因する問題の場合、修正できない可能性があります。"

#. TRANSLATORS: in reference to firmware protection: 1/4 stars
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-dialog.c:111
#: panels/privacy/firmware-security/cc-firmware-security-page.c:458
